Class MuseumRoom

java.lang.Object
greenfoot.World
Room
MuseumRoom
public class MuseumRoom extends Room
MuseumRoom is the room where all the action takes place. It is utter chaos in this newly opened museum and thus highly suspectible to robbery despite the museums dreams to become one of the biggst.
